Text: Story is all about we get life once and never given again . life is all about
  seeing new things and trying new cuisine meeting new people living the to the most
  and not regretting anything . .. Just each and every day like its the last day of
  our life .. Loving the nature and looking for new species under water . Life is
  all about new experiences new life and new people life is amazing but its short
